# NordicWebFlow — Cloudflare Pages URL routing
# NOTE: Cloudflare Pages serves .html files at clean URLs automatically.
# We only need special redirects here — NOT rules for existing pages.

# .dk → .com redirect is handled via Cloudflare Redirect Rules (not here)
# See README for setup instructions.

# Danish character URL → ASCII slug
/ejendomsm%C3%A6gler  /ejendomsmaegler  301
/ejendomsmægler        /ejendomsmaegler  301

# Legacy redirects
/home           /               301
/pricing        /priser         301
/contact        /kontakt        301

# 404 fallback
/*              /404.html       404
